(436, '368.1', '2', '343', '698', 'No mss.', '[JC: a possible ms (?in Turkish?) is Nurosmaniye 2316 listed in the Turkish catalogue as Levakıhü\'l-Envari\'l-Kudsiyye el-Müntekat mine\'l-Fütuhati\'l-Me. On the other hand a very similar title is attributed to eş-Şa\'rani (d. 973H) in Fatih 2804 (although here there could be confusion with the latter\'s work Levakihu\'l-Envar fi Tabakati\'l-Ahyar which is found in around 60 Turkish mss). Also Cambridge Browne D.9 contains a copy of Kitāb al-kibrīt al-aḥmar fī bayān ʻulūm al-kashf al-akbar by Shaʿrānī said in the catalogue http://www.fihrist.org.uk/ to be an abridgement of the work by the same author entitled Lawāqiḥ al-anwār al-qudsīyah, which is, in turn, an abridgement of al-Futūḥāt al-makkīyah of IA. Similar info is supplied in British Library SAL 1380 (for IO Delhi 1844).] [In Cairo National (dated 1318H) there is a work attributed to Ibn Sawdakīn with the variant title Lawāqiḥ al-asrār wa-lawāʾiḥ al-anwār  (لواقح الاسرار ولوائح الانوار). C. Addas has identified an earlier one in Budeiri, Palestine: http://www.e-corpus.org/eng/search/results/117688-%D9%84%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%82%D8%AD-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%B1-%D9%88%D9%84%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%8A%D8%AD-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%86%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%B1.html. And we find yet another copy of that in Tunisian National Library (http://www.bnt.nat.tn/) A-Mss-04296(1)] [JC: a late ms (1318H) with title Lawāqiḥ al-asrār wa-lawāʾiḥ al-anwār again linked with Ibn Sawdakīn is available online at http://www.ibnarabi.net/books.php?a=1 - under title - لواقح الأسرار ولوائح الأنوار للشيخ العارف سيدي ابن سويدكين من كلام الشيخ الأكبر قدس سره . SH finds (personal communication 13.09.2015) that this ms is related to but different from RG 436 Wasa\'il al-masa\'il of Ibn Sawdakin in Berlin we 1735. Since this is dated 1318H it could well be this ms is the Cairo National ms tas. 147] [JC: Damascus, al-Assad 16632 and also al-Assad 16627/2 each contain a work of Ibn Sawdakīn entitled Lawāqiḥ al-asrār wa-lawāmiḥ al-anwār ]', 'OY_OIL_BP189_Ara_Y_all_v2_1_RG_entries.pdf', '5', 'R', 'K. Lawāqiḥ al-anwār wa-lawāmiḥ al-asrār', 'K. Lawāqiḥ al-anwār wa-lawāmiḥ al-asrār (698)<br/>Lawāqiḥ al-asrār wa-lawāʾiḥ al-anwār (699)<br/>', 'كتاب لواقح الأنوار ولوامح الأسرار', 'كتاب لواقح الأنوار ولوامح الأسرار<br/>لواقح الأسرار ولوائح الأنوار<br/>', '<table class=\"tab_mrm_compare_titles\"><tr> <td width=50% dir=\"ltr\" class=\"tab_val\">K. Lawāqiḥ al-anwār wa-lawāmiḥ al-asrār</td> <td dir=\"ltr\" class=\"tab_fill\">&nbsp;</td><td width=50% class=\"tab_val_right\" dir=\"rtl\">كتاب لواقح الأنوار ولوامح الأسرار</td> </tr><tr> <td width=50% dir=\"ltr\" class=\"tab_val\">Lawāqiḥ al-asrār wa-lawāʾiḥ al-anwār</td> <td dir=\"ltr\" class=\"tab_fill\">&nbsp;</td><td width=50% class=\"tab_val_right\" dir=\"rtl\">لواقح الأسرار ولوائح الأنوار</td> </tr></table>'),
