(717, '605.1', '2', '432', '1135', 'No mss. Printed in Tehran 1315H.', '[JC: the dissertation The Quest for a Universal Science...” (2012) by Matthew S. Melvin-Koushki available at https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Sain_al-Din_Turka_Isfahani gives further info. against work Tamhīd al-Qawāʿid or al-Tamhīd fī Sharḥ Qawāʿid al-Tawḥīd by Ṣāʾin al-Dīn Turka al-Iṣfahānī : Lithograph 413, 234 pp., Mishkāt Collection, Central Library, Tehran University (Dānishgāh), constituting the printing by Aḥmad Shīrāzī of 1315/1898, edited and commented upon by Shādravān Mīrzā Yad Allāh Naẓar-i Pāk Kujūrī. The volume also includes the Miftāḥ Mafātīḥ al-Fuṣūṣ al-Musammā bi-l-Nuṣūṣ of Ṣadr al-Dīn Qūnavī, the R. Vaḥdat-i Vujūd of Āqā Mīrzā Muḥammad Qumshaʾī (written in reference to the first section of Qayṣarī’s commentary on the Fuṣūṣ), and a R. Ithnā-ʿashariyya [RG 605.1] attributed to Ibn ʿArabī, and in the margin the R. Ṭarīq al-Taṣawwuf of Ibn ʿArabī (written at the request of Fakhr al-Dīn Rāzī) [RG 612?] and the Miftāḥ al-Ghayb of Qūnavī.]', 'OY_OIL_BP189_Ara_Y_all_v2_2_RG_entries.pdf', '27', 'L', 'Risāla al-ithnaʿashar imām al-mansūbā ilā al-Shaykh Muḥyi al-Dīn b. al-ʿArabī', 'Risāla al-ithnaʿashar imām al-mansūbā ilā al-Shaykh Muḥyi al-Dīn b. al-ʿArabī (1135)<br/>', 'رسالة الاثنا عشر إماما المنسوبة إلى الشيخ محيى الدين بن العربى', 'رسالة الاثنا عشر إماما المنسوبة إلى الشيخ محيى الدين بن العربى<br/>', '<table class=\"tab_mrm_compare_titles\"><tr> <td width=50% dir=\"ltr\" class=\"tab_val\">Risāla al-ithnaʿashar imām al-mansūbā ilā al-Shaykh Muḥyi al-Dīn b. al-ʿArabī</td> <td dir=\"ltr\" class=\"tab_fill\">&nbsp;</td><td width=50% class=\"tab_val_right\" dir=\"rtl\">رسالة الاثنا عشر إماما المنسوبة إلى الشيخ محيى الدين بن العربى</td> </tr></table>'),
