(9039, '150.90091', '1', '244', '9039', 'Commentary upon RG 150 by Simnānī (d. 736H)', '[JC: for same man\'s commentary upon FM see RG 135.9021. Cambridge D.8 contains discourses in Persian by this same Rukn al-Dīn ʻAlāʼ al-Dawlah Simnānī  = Aḥmad ibn Muḥammad (d.736H) - Maqālāt-i Shaykh Rukn al-Dawlah ʻAlāʼ al-Dīn Simnānī - discourses which mention Shaykh Sadr al-din, Sa\'d al-din Hamawi, and IA - see http://www.fihrist.org.uk/profile/work/0ea35635-3ce2-4907-98db-f968f651f3db and http://www.lib.cam.ac.uk/arabic_catalogues/nicholson1932/full/CUL005_028r.jpg . See also his 40 discourses in Cambridge D.21 (f.90-111) Risalah-i chihil majlis http://www.fihrist.org.uk/profile/work/f7882f30-ae4f-46b0-a384-0f3df2ebf1d0 and http://www.lib.cam.ac.uk/arabic_catalogues/nicholson1932/full/CUL005_033r.jpg . Said to be a Kubrawi  opponent of IA see: http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/ala-al-dawla-semnani (which refers to other works of his)]', 'OY_OIL_BP189_Ara_Y_all_v1_1_RG_entries.pdf', '55', 'L', 'Sharḥ fuṣūṣ al-ḥikam', 'Sharḥ fuṣūṣ al-ḥikam (9039)<br/>', 'شرح فصوص الحكم', 'شرح فصوص الحكم<br/>', '<table class=\"tab_mrm_compare_titles\"><tr> <td width=50% dir=\"ltr\" class=\"tab_val\">Sharḥ fuṣūṣ al-ḥikam</td> <td dir=\"ltr\" class=\"tab_fill\">&nbsp;</td><td width=50% class=\"tab_val_right\" dir=\"rtl\">شرح فصوص الحكم</td> </tr></table>'),
